================== Conway's Game of Life implemented in CUDA =========================


  ==================== Andrew Pappas sID: 1115201500201 ==========================

Compile:
==========
    nvcc life.cu -o life 

Run:
====
    ./life [dimensions][generations]
        
        example: ./life 10 5 

        will generate a 10x10 grid of 5 Time Steps (generations).

=================================  Thank you! ==================================        
